title: Open a test project in Katalon Studio - Platform Edition
description: For Katalon Studio - Platform Edition, you need to set up your project on Katalon TestOps, then open your test project in Katalon Studio - Platform Edition.Note: You cannot create a new project in Katalon Studio - Platform Edition.
